Do's
Keep your profile professional and accurate
Think before you post — consider how it reflects on you
Use privacy settings to control who sees your posts
Credit others when sharing their content
Report suspicious accounts or harmful content



Don'ts
Never share personal details like phone number or address publicly
"Avoid posting offensive, hateful, or misleading content"
Do not accept friend/connection requests from strangers you cannot verify
Never engage in cyberbullying or online harassment
Avoid oversharing your location or daily routine online
